观看埃里卡·巴杜（Erykah Badu）向罗伯塔·弗拉克（Roberta Flack）致敬https://www.nme.com/news/music/erykah-badu-pays-tribute-to-roberta-to-to-roberta-flack-at-intimate-london-dj-nondon-dj-set-3842345?u tm_source = rss＆utm_medium = rss＆utm_campaign = erykah-badu-pays-tribute-to-roberta-to-roberta-flack-flack-tim-london-dj-stetKyann-Sian Williams Wed, 05 Mar 2025 11:01:06 +0000 Music NewsNewsR&BSoul https://www.nme.com/?p=3842345 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/erykah-badu-2000x1270-neotookthat.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Erykah Badu Djing在2025年2月在伦敦的爵士咖啡馆（Lone Jazz Cafe）的DJ lo lo lo lo lo lo lo lo lo to。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/erykah-badu-2000x1270-neotookthat.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/erykah-badu-2000x1270-neotookthat-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/erykah-badu-2000x1270-neotookthat-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/erykah-badu-2000x1270-neotookthat-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/erykah-badu-2000x1270-neotookthat-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/erykah-badu-2000x1270-neotookthat-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>灵魂传奇还揭示了她的喜剧梦想，以及她对Yasiin Bey的“ Umi Said”的想法，迎来了她54岁生日</p><p>邮政<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/erykah-badu-pays-tribute-to-roberta-flack-at-intimate-london-dj-set-3842345">观看埃里卡·巴杜（Erykah Badu）向伦敦亲密DJ套装的罗伯塔·弗拉克（Roberta Flack）致敬，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/erykah-badu-2000x1270-neotookthat.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Erykah Badu Djing在2025年2月在伦敦的爵士咖啡馆（Lone Jazz Cafe）的DJ lo lo lo lo lo lo lo lo lo to。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/erykah-badu-2000x1270-neotookthat.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/erykah-badu-2000x1270-neotookthat-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/erykah-badu-2000x1270-neotookthat-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/erykah-badu-2000x1270-neotookthat-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/erykah-badu-2000x1270-neotookthat-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/erykah-badu-2000x1270-neotookthat-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/erykah-badu">埃里卡·巴杜（Erykah Badu）</a>在伦敦的一次DJ生日那天在伦敦举行的一次DJ期间向已故的伟大歌手兼作词人Roberta Flack致敬。请参阅下面的视频。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/killing-me-softly-icon-roberta-flack-dies-age-88-3840842">“杀死我”偶像罗伯塔·弗拉克（Roberta Flack）死亡，年龄88</a></strong></li></ul><p>上周四（2月27日），巴杜（Badu）在卡姆登（Camden）的爵士咖啡馆（Jazz Cafe）播放了一个惊喜的DJ庆祝她的54岁生日，在别名dj lo down loretta brown下。</p><p>伦敦自己的Keyrahh是开幕式的DJ，当“ Bag Lady”歌手上台时，她感谢她为人群的热身，并介绍了Rashad Smith（又名制片人掷骰子），她称呼她为“来自纽约的最初的Hitmaker，来自纽约的最初的Hitmaker，这是90年代街上的街道上的最初杀手”。</p><p>然后，她在“蘑菇”上接管了甲板，进行实验性的折衷套装。</p><p>后来的即兴问答环节。一位粉丝赞扬了德克萨斯歌手2012年<a href="/artists/robert-glasper">罗伯特·格拉斯珀（Robert Glasper）</a>合作“ Afro Blue”的Badu，他的“黑色广播”专辑中导致Badu指出歌词最初是由Flack撰写的。</p><p> “罗伯塔！”巴杜开始大喊麦克风。 “罗伯塔！ […]有人说我们可以遇到两次某些死亡：第一次死亡是我们停止呼吸并停止生活在地球上的死亡。第二次死亡是最后一次有人说你的名字，罗伯塔！”</p><p>然后，她发行了歌曲，唱着Flack的标志性热门歌曲“用他的歌轻柔地杀死我”，然后扔了一个和平标志并离开。在此处查看镜头： </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DGnxwyyIt0g/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="backgroun