k" rel="noopener">official description</a> . “It&#39;s weird, it&#39;s wild, and it&#39;s designed to be shared.” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="分裂小说| Official Gameplay Reveal Trailer" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/fcwngWPXQtg?start=2&enablejsapi=1#038;feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> <em>Split Fiction</em> is released tomorrow (March 6) for PlayStation 5, Xbox Series X/S and PC. According to aggregator site <a href="https://www.metacritic.com/browse/game/all/all/current-year/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Metacritic</em></a> , <em>Split Fiction</em> is the best reviewed game of 2025 so far, with a score of 91.</p><p> The second best reviewed game of the year is <em>Monster Hunter Wilds</em> , which launched last week and sold more than 8million copies in just three days, with <em>Kingdom Come Deliverance 2</em> , <em>Lonely Mountains: Snow Riders</em> and <em>Citizen Sleeper 2</em> rounding out the Top Five.</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">拆分小说是迄今为止2025年收视率最高的游戏（91）。 <a href="https://t.co/DpzxcpJbSQ">pic.twitter.com/DpzxcpJbSQ</a></p><p> — GermanStrands (@GermanStrands) <a href="https://twitter.com/GermanStrands/status/1896986597738094923?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">March 4, 2025</a> </p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p> “ <em>Split Fiction</em> is a generational work. It&#39;s brimming with creativity, tells a resonant story that reflects the current state of the world, and is a sincere love letter to genre fiction that has inspired so many of us,” wrote <a href="https://www.inverse.com/gaming/split-fiction-review" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Inverse</a> in their five-star review. “Everything feels so polished, and is executed with such confidence and style that it&#39;s impossible not to fall in love with it. There&#39;s really nothing else quite like <em>Split Fiction</em> in games today,” reads <em><a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/split-fiction-review" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Eurogamer</a></em> &#39;s glowing review.</p><p> Responding to the critical acclaim, game director Josef Fares <a href="https://x.com/josef_fares/status/1896980860907479487" target="_blank" rel="noopener">wrote</a> : “This is amazing. Can&#39;t wait for everyone to play it.”</p><p> In other news, <em>Tony Hawk&#39;s Pro Skater 3+4</em> has officially been announced, with <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/tony-hawks-pro-skater-3-4-release-date-pre-order-soundtrack-3843716">the remastered skating game coming this summer.</a></p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/split-fiction-best-game-2025-reviews-3843724">&#39;Split Fiction&#39; is the best reviewed game of 2025 so far</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
